snippet: Falling oil prices hardly seem to be bothering the two biggest U.S. oil companies, but things could get tougher in the coming months....

headline.print_headline: Exxon, Chevron Shrug Off Effect of Low Oil Prices
headline.main: Exxon, Chevron Shrug Off Effect of Low Oil Prices

lead_paragraph: Falling oil prices hardly seem to be bothering the two biggest U.S. oil companies, but things could get tougher in the coming months.
